videos.headline: Iowa's dominance continues with 42-yard TD
videos.description: C.J. Beathard Iowa QB C.J. Beathard finds Riley McCarron for a 42-yard touchdown to continue put the Hawkeyes up by three scores over Purdue.

videos.headline: Iowa RB Wadley races through Purdue's defense for 75-yard TD
videos.description: Iowa RB Akrum Wadley zips straight through Purdue's defensive front and runs 75 yards for the score, putting the Hawkeyes up 35-7.
